        {
            "title": "順豐收入增8% 首破三千億",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"順豐收入增8% 首破三千億\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/yMYf99k0HLJ5T.wTIXIFTg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-03/70182370-2c97-11f1-bf76-e59b33f87eb8\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">順豐收入增8% 首破三千億</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
