        {
            "title": "MSCI亞太指數抹去今年以來15%的漲幅 通膨及經濟放緩擔憂打擊市場情緒",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 亞洲股市下跌，該地區主要基準指數抹去了今年的漲幅，因伊朗戰爭導致能源成本飆升引發通膨及經濟成長放緩的擔憂。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">周二，MSCI亞太指數一度下跌1.3%，其中三星電子和SK海力士對該指數的拖累最大。MSCI新興市場指數也抹去了2026年的漲幅。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這一里程碑凸顯出亞洲市場命運的急劇轉變。年初時，隨著投資者持續湧入該地區的人工智能基礎設施股票，亞洲市場曾一路走高。隨著中東衝突進入第五周，風險押注正在減少。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-3d2075bf-a0ab-3db1-986d-7a97aef6016c-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">MSCI亞太指數曾於2月27日創下紀錄新高，自年初漲幅達到15%，遠超全球股市表現。隨著市場預期貨幣政策將收緊且關鍵原物料供應受限，投資者開始重新審視成長理論，此前積累的漲幅已蒸發殆盡。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">有鑒於對中東國家進口能源的高度依賴，包括韓國、日本和印度在內的亞洲經濟體特別容易受到原油的衝擊。這使得交易員擔憂成本上升對企業利潤以及為抑制通膨而加息可能帶來的負面影響。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Asian Stocks Wipe Out 2026 Gains as War Drives Inflation Worries</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Sangmi Cha.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/msci%E4%BA%9E%E5%A4%AA%E6%8C%87%E6%95%B8%E6%8A%B9%E5%8E%BB%E4%BB%8A%E5%B9%B4%E4%BB%A5%E4%BE%8615-%E7%9A%84%E6%BC%B2%E5%B9%85-%E9%80%9A%E8%86%A8%E5%8F%8A%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E6%94%BE%E7%B7%A9%E6%93%94%E6%86%82%E6%89%93%E6%93%8A%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4%E6%83%85%E7%B7%92-003524235.html",
